After having and enjoying both 60 and 90 min iPad's this was a must. The addition of the Syrah grape must to the traditional 60 min ipa is awesome. It adds an extra complexity to a good beer. The aroma is great for an ipa and the flavor following is just as good

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

A very rewarding sour. Have it with a savory dish or desert. The aroma and flavor are both reminiscent of a sweet vinegar and goes down very smooth
